:

1. *Luk* je veoma zdrav za jedenje. (Onion is very healthy to eat.)
2. Volela bih da je *luk* uključen u ovu salatu. (I would like for onion to be included in this salad.)
3. *Lukom* obično začinjavamo meso. (We usually season meat with onion.)
4. Moja majka voli da kuva sa puno *luka*. (My mother loves to cook with a lot of onion.)
5. Moj tata uvek dodaje malo *luka* u sve što kuva. (My dad always adds a little onion to everything he cooks.)